    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Any project is a temporary endeavor that must end on a given day. A project is an investment in a business objective or in some change initiative that is valuable from the sponsor’s perspective. The project’s output needs to justify the money spent by the sponsor and time and energy spent by other stakeholders. Projects should not be done just to keep an organization or person happy or busy.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
